"center\">21</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Twenty-one</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiuno</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">22</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Twenty-two</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintidós</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">23</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Twenty-three</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintitrés</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">24</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Twenty-four</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinticuatro</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">25</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Twenty-five</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinticinco</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">26</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Twenty-six</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiséis</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">27</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Twenty-seven</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintisiete</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">28</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Twenty-eight</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiocho</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">29</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Twenty-nine</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintinueve</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br>\n<h2>Brojevi sa akcentima</h2>\n<p>Veoma je važno da nastavite sa vežbanjem sa sledećim brojevima jer imaju znake naglaska:</p>\n<p>16 - <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Dieciséis</span></p>\n<p>22 - <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintidós</span></p>\n<p>23 - <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintitrés</span></p>\n<p>26 - <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiséis</span></p>\n<br>\n<h2><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiuno</span> protiv <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiún</span></h2>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiuno</span> je puni oblik broja 21. Koristi se kada se ova reč koristi kao samostalna imenica ili kada se govori o brojevima koji nisu direktno povezani sa drugom imenicom. Primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">El resultado es veintiuno</span> - Rezultat je dvadeset i jedan.</p>\n<p>Suprotno tome, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veintiún</span> koristi se kada reč prethodi i modifikuje mušku imenicu. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tengo veintiún años</span> - Nina imam dvadeset i jedna godine.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da reč <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veintiún</span> ima naglasak na slovo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>.</p>\n</section>",
